{"article_id":"iZYNCAJxP684s8yt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Hillary Clinton strikes a defiant tone on Benghazi in her upcoming memoir `` Hard Choices ''","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"and knocks those `` who exploit '' the September 11 , 2012 terrorist attack as `` a political tool , ''","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"according to a Politico report on the chapter .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The former secretary of state also writes","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that the attack","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"which Republicans have used","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"to bludgeon Clinton","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"since the U.S. ambassador to Libya and three other Americans were killed in the incident-","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"is surrounded by a `` regrettable amount of misinformation , speculation , and flat-out deceit by some in politics and the media . ''","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Politico obtained the chapter ahead of a Friday confab","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"where Democratic national security experts and communicators will be briefed on Benghazi by Philippe Reines , a longtime Clinton adviser and spokesman .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"House Republicans have continued to pressure Clinton on Benghazi","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"and earlier this month organized a select committee","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to investigate the terrorist attack .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Democrats contend","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that the investigation is nothing more than a political tool","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"to criticize Clinton","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"as she mulls a run at the presidency in 2016 .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"While it is likely that Republicans will call on Clinton to testify before the select committee ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Clinton casts doubt on her participation in the investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"according to the report by Politico 's Maggie Haberman ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"who is also a CNN political analyst","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"`` I will not be a part of a political slugfest on the backs of dead Americans , ''","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Clinton writes .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"`` It 's just plain wrong ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and it 's unworthy of our great country .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Those","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"who insist on politicizing the tragedy","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"will have to do so without me . ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"She continues to knock House Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"writing","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"while she respects the oversight role of Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"`` many of these same people are a broken record about unanswered questions .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"But there is a difference between unanswered questions and unlistened to answers . ''","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"GOP chairman of Select Benghazi Committee reacts to Hillary Clinton book chapter","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"The U.S. consulate in Benghazi was attacked on September 11 , 2012 .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Four Americans ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"including Ambassador Chris Stevens ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"were killed .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Initially , the attack was thought to be perpetrated by an angry mob","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"responding to a video","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"made in the U.S.","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"which mocked Islam and the Prophet Mohammed ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"but was later determined to be a terrorist attack .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Questions about Benghazi have dogged Clinton since the attack","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and some have questioned","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"whether the former first lady is to blame for Stevens ' death","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"- the first U.S. ambassador","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"killed on duty in over 30 years .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Earlier this year , Clinton said","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that Benghazi was her biggest regret during the four years","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"she served as America 's top diplomat .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"`` It was a terrible tragedy","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"losing four Americans , two diplomats","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"and now it is public","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"so I can say","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"two CIA operatives , ''","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"Clinton said at a speech in New Orleans .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Clinton has also taken responsibility for the deaths","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"and did so ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"according to Politico ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"in the memoir chapter , too .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"`` As Secretary I was the one ultimately responsible for my people 's safety ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and I never felt that responsibility more deeply","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"than I did that day , ''","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"she writes .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Clinton testified about the attack in House and Senate hearings in 2013 .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Republicans , however , say","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"there are still questions left unanswered","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"and some contend","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"that the attack should disqualify the former secretary of state from holding future office .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"According to Politico ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Clinton responds to some Republican questions on Benghazi ,","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"including claims","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"that military assets were not scrambled in time","depth":16},{"id":78,"text":"to aid the compound","depth":16},{"id":79,"text":"and that requests for more security for the compound were ignored by the secretary of state .","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"`` Our military does everything humanly possible","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"to save American lives","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"- and would do more","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"if they could , ''","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"Clinton writes","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"according to Politico .","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"`` That anyone has ever suggested otherwise","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"is something","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"I will never understand . ''","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"The former first lady also defends then-U.S . Ambassador to the United Nations Susan Rice ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"who used five Sunday talk show appearances soon after the attack","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"to link the deaths to the anti-Islam video","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"posted to YouTube .","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"`` Susan stated","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"what the intelligence community believed , rightly or wrongly , at the time , ''","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"Clinton writes ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"according to Politico .","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"`` That was the best","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"she or anyone could do . ''","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"Republicans contend","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"that the talking points","depth":17},{"id":101,"text":"that link the attack to the video","depth":17},{"id":102,"text":"show","depth":16},{"id":103,"text":"the White House was playing politics with Benghazi","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"because President Barack Obama 's 2012 re-election was just two months away .","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"As to why Rice rather than Clinton appeared on the Sunday shows ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Clinton writes ,","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"`` I do n't see appearing on Sunday-morning television as any more of a responsibility","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"than appearing on late-night TV .","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"Only in Washington is the definition","depth":17},{"id":110,"text":"of talking to Americans","depth":17},{"id":111,"text":"confined to 9 A.M. on Sunday mornings . ''","depth":16},{"id":112,"text":"CNN confirmed","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"that Tommy Vietor , a National Security Council spokesman during Obama 's first term , has been brought on by the Clinton team","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"to coordinate and assist in the response to the book .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"The hiring of Vietor ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"whose time with the President dates back to Obama ' s days in the Senate","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"and who has ties to both Clinton and Obama 's closest advisers ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"signals a closer cooperation between the White House and Clinton 's staff on communicating the news from Clinton 's book .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"In another sign of stepped up cooperation , Democratic surrogates and communicators","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"who publicly support both Obama and Clinton","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"met at the White House this week with Communications Director Jenn Palmieri and Deputy National Security Adviser for Strategic Communications Ben Rhodes","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"to talk about a number of issues ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"including Benghazi and Clinton 's upcoming book ,","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"according to a source familiar with the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"While the topic was not on the official meeting agenda ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"one surrogate asked about it","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"and the President ' s aides made clear","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"they want no daylight between Obama and Clinton on foreign policy issues","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"as the book rolls out ,","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"the source added .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"The messaging ,","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"the White House aides said","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"according to the source ,","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"is this :","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Obama ' s team of rivals became an unrivaled team .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"In addition to working with the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"the Clinton camp has stepped up their messaging around the book 's release","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"to include a coordinated surrogate operation .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Clinton 's team ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"according to a source familiar with the book rollout ,","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"has tapped Kiki McLean , a former Clinton senior adviser and veteran of five presidential campaigns ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"to coordinate the surrogate operation .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"This group includes a war room of former diplomats","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"who stand ready to respond to criticism of Clinton ' s tenure at the State Department ,","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"according to the source .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"During an interview","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"that aired Friday on `` Live with Kelly and Michael , ''","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"Obama spoke highly of Clinton","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"if she chooses to run for president ,","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"he thinks","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"she `` would be very effective at that . ''","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"`` I always admired her .","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"As soon as she got here ,","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"she could n't have been more effective , more loyal , ''","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"Obama said .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"`` And since that time we have become really , really good friends . ''","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"The President 's comments come","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"a day after Obama and Clinton had an `` informal , private '' lunch at the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"according to a White House official .","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"Republicans were quick to respond to Clinton 's chapter on Benghazi .","depth":6},{"id":162,"text":"Republican National Committee Chairman Reince Priebus told CNN on Friday","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"that the Benghazi chapter shows","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"`` Hillary Clinton , President Obama and the Democrats would rather blame Republicans","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"for asking questions","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"than get answers for Americans . ''","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"`` It isn ' t acceptable for the Democrats to try to sweep this under the rug , ''","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Priebus said .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"`` Americans want answers","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"so it doesn ' t happen again . ''","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"Tim Miller , the executive director of America Rising , an anti-Clinton super PAC , added in an email to reporters","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"that `` Clinton offers plenty of finger-pointing but no real accountability","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"of what she should 've done differently/better . ''","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"`` In a 34-page recounting of her actions before and after a deadly terrorist attack , it appears Clinton offers few if any real regrets","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"about how she handled the attack , ''","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"Miller said .","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"`` Hard Choices '' is an important moment for Clinton , the current favorite","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"to win the 2016 Democratic presidential nomination","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"should she run .","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"Critics have charged","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"that her time as America 's top diplomat was marked by a lack of a crowning achievement ,","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"while Clinton confidants have looked to frame those years as a success","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"and see the book as the most potent way","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"to do that .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"Clinton has said","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"the book begins with her accepting Obama 's offer","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"to become secretary of state","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"and covers a range of topics ,","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"including Iran , Syria and Libya .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"She has joked","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"that the memoir will be `` just another light summer read ''","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"and will cover topics from `` Crimea to climate change . ''","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"Asked why the Benghazi chapter was released prior to the overall release of the book ,","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"Clinton spokesman Nick Merrill told CNN","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"that `` until the book is released ,","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"there ' s nothing","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"to say .","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"once it ' s released ,","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"it will speak for itself . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":401,"left":0,"right":400,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":400,"left":237,"right":399,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":212,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":210,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":203,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":202,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":4,"right":208,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":208,"left":207,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":207,"left":5,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":6,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":204,"right":9,"re